---
title: "What a Knowledge Leverage Score Reveals About Your Team's Operational Efficiency"
date: "2023-08-21"
summary: "Measure knowledge leverage to understand operational efficiency. The score reveals whether your team can scale or is stuck."
coverImage: ""
tags:
